<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I have heard alot of rumors(unconfirmed) at this point about the Warrios Particle Weapon which I believe is entitled Heart and Soul.  What I have heard is that it is either a 2hs weapon  red on one side and blue on the other,  or with the use of the scabbard u can separate the sword into 2 1hs weapons, one is Heart and one is Soul.  I have seen some screeshots, but I have not seen any stats, or heard of anyone finishing the quest.  I have heard that the Quest starts in EK.  If anybody knows more about our fine new weapon, please give us a post.<hr>Drambuie Twinblade<br>
Warrior of The Brothers of Darkness (the Nameless)</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
